試播集與其他集數皆於[[德克薩斯州|德州]][[奧斯汀|奧斯汀]]拍攝，而故事背景則是設定在[[加利福尼亞州|加州]][[莫德斯托_(加利福尼亞州)|莫德斯托]][[中央谷地|中央谷地]]。<ref>{{cite web |last=Rowland |first=Marijke |url=http://www.modbee.com/2014/06/22/3404379/abc-crime-drama-will-be-set-in.html |title=ABC crime drama will be set in Modesto; local reaction mixed |work=The Modesto Bee |date=2014-06-22 |accessdate=2014-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808041124/http://www.modbee.com/2014/06/22/3404379/abc-crime-drama-will-be-set-in.html |archive-date=2014-08-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

